pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Ebiwandiiko ebiragiddwa ku dashiboodi eno bikunganyizibwa butereevu okuva mu by’okuddamu mu kunoonyereza era tebiva mu bibalo by’amawanga ebitongole oba ebikwata ku biwandiiko. Kikiikirira endowooza abavubuka ze baalaga mu kiseera ky’okunoonyereza, era ebimalirizo byonna ebiggiddwa mu by’okuddamu bino bivunaanyizibwa ku mukozesa, so si PMNCH. PMNCH yeewaddeyo okussa ekitiibwa, okutumbula n’okukuuma eddembe n’obulamu obulungi bw’abantu bonna ssekinnoomu. Endowooza zonna eziragiddwa mu by’okuddamu mu kunoonyereza oba ebiwandiiko ebifulumiziddwa ebifulumye okuva mu daasiboodi eno ebikontana n’obweyamo buno tebikkirizibwa PMNCH.
